[background arg="#000000ff" fade="1.3"]
[background arg="res://Assets/Backgrounds/DSCN0888.JPG" fade="0.6"]
As I walk through the gate I am met with another indivdiual. There body seemingly shifting constantly.
They up from the patch of grass they had been observing.
join "Big thing" left [animation="Fade In Down"]
audio music "res://Assets/Audio/01 - The Dream Starts.mp3" [volume="-4.4" loop="true"]
???: ...oh? You made it here sooner than we thought you would.
???: Personally I was betting on you being here in another 30 minutes...
- Who are you?
	Not_Important: Our name is not important...
	Not_Important: ...really now?
	That's better.
- You were betting on me?
	oh yes? Not much to do otherwise...get's boring waiting on you to show up.
label Big Convo
But yes..you made it. That is good we are proud of you.
Last time you dreamt something similar you got lost a third the way through...
- Last time?
	Oh yes. This style is a reocurring dream of your's. Personally I think you read those dream books of ours to many times but hey, We don't judge here.
	Let me guess? You had a shitty day at work and have let things slip again? What was it this time?
	- I don't need to tell you
		Oh you want to be snippy now?
		Why am I not surprised...trying to push me away won't work you know?
		On account of us being a part of [i]your[/i] dream world.
	- It was the bed...
		The bed? Figures...it's always something small with you huh?
		You got to remember your limits...but again we do not judge.
		Even then that is not important to the now. What matters now is you want to wake up, and you are almost able to.
		Behind me is a bed. You just have to slide into it and you'll wake up.
		That should be something you can do I am sure.
		- Thank you
			Oh? leaving so soon? I am not surprised.
			Before you go wondering off again, let me tell you a few things.
		- Why are you here exactly?
			oh come on, you are dreaming yes? Surely you can figure it out by now.
			I am you and you are me...you know this song and dance I'm sure.
			Same as the rest of ths "cast" you have conjured up.
label judge
You have a fun way of treating those around you don't you?
Starlight, Red, Steve...all little aspects your brain has conjured up for one night only...or however dreams work.
So let's see how you treated them...
{Starlight_Outcome}, {Red_Outcome}.
and {Steve_Outcome}...
if {Red_Outcome} == "You left out Starlights apoloagy which left Red in a rage.":
	You treated them quite poorly if I were to say so myself.
	I would dare to say you made things worst for them as a whole.
	I got to say if [i]this[/i] is how you treat the aborations around you...
	Maybe you deserve your lot in life.
	But as I have said. We do not judge here.
	You may leave now. As I put yourself into the bed and you'll wake up.
	Oh and when you wake up...please look into a new fridge the one you have is absolutly disgusting.
	Goodbye {MC}.
	set {Bad_Ending} = true
	set {Ending} = true
	do SceneManager.change_scene("res://Final_area_3.tscn")
	[end_timeline]
elif {Red_Outcome} == "You told Red the truth, they can move past the distrust that they felt towards Starlight.":
	You treated those around you with a facit of kindness.
	Despite knowing that none of this is real you took the time to listen to them, to [i]care[/i] for them.
	It's...I am a little surprised, but in a good way.
	Maybe you are not the disgusting monster you view yourself as {MC}.
	You may leave now. As I said the bed will take you out of the dream.
	Take care of yourself {MC}
	set {Good_Ending} = true
	set {Ending} = true
	do SceneManager.change_scene("res://Final_area_3.tscn")
	[end_timeline]